def bubble_sort(arr):
    n = len(arr)
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(0, n - i - 1):
            if arr[j] > arr[j + 1]:
                arr[j], arr[j + 1] = arr[j + 1], arr[j]
    return arr

arr = [99, 3, 6, 1, 9, 13, 73, 63, 7, 8, 52]
print(" :", arr)
bubble_sort(arr)
print(" :", arr)
